snippet.title: Ace Combat Joint Assault - PSP - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
An insight into the plot behind the story of ACE COMBAT JOINT ASSAULT is unveiled along with new furious and raging 4-player action. The next episode of the ACE COMBAT Action Series will land in your palm and on the PSP (Playstation Portable) in Summer 2010.

Check out your local Namco Bandai website for more information on our other titles: http://www.namcobandaigames.eu/
